  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.4.1">
<l>orukuṟaḷā yirunilammū vaṭimaṇ vēṇṭi yulakaṉaittu mīraṭiyā loṭukki yoṉṟum</l>
<l>tarukaveṉā māvaliyaic ciṟaiyil vaittatāṭāḷaṉ tāḷaṇaivīr takka kīrtti</l>
<l>yarumaṟaiyiṉ tiraḷnāṉkum vēḷvi yaintu maṅkaṅka ḷavaiyāṟu micaika ḷēḻum</l>
<l>teruvilmali viḻāvaḷamum ciṟakkum kāḻic cīrāma viṇṇakarē cērmi ṉīrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who would touch the feet of the one of powerful feet</l>
<l rend="indent">who put Māvali in prison,</l>
<l>Having, as one dwarf, requested the two-fold land in three feet of earth,</l>
<l rend="indent">having compressed the entire world in two steps, while saying,</l>
<l rend="indent">“Give me one [more]”!</l>
<l>Gather you [all] at Cīrāmaviṇṇakaram in Kāḻi which is distinguished by</l>
<l rend="indent">the riches of crowded street festivals,</l>
<l>The four collections of the rare Vedas, deserved of fame, the five sacrifices,</l>
<l rend="indent">the six branches [of knowledge], and seven [modes of] music.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
